<MELItem itemNbr="21-54-02" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-21-54-02.1.2-21-54-02">
<Title>Forward Cargo Air Conditioning (FCAC) Boost Fan (787-9: VN-A861, VN-A862, VN-A863, VN-A864, VN-A865, VN-A866, VN-A867, VN-A868, VN-A869, VN-A870, VN-A871)</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>FCAC boost fan is deactivated.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Forward cargo electric heater is deactivated.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>FCAC remains OFF.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate FCAC boost fan and forward cargo electric heater (AMM DDG 21-54-02).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Deactivate FCAC boost fan:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the following circuit breakers and lock with an INOP tag:</Para>
<List listType="1)">
<ListItem>
<Para>MC-FCAC BOOST FAN</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>BOOST FAN-FCAC</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Gain access to boost fan.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Disconnect, cap and stow electrical connector to the boost fan.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Deactivate forward cargo electric heater:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the following circuit breakers and lock with an INOP tag:</Para>
<List listType="1)">
<Effectivities>
<Effectivity>For 787-9:</Effectivity>
</Effectivities>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER-FWD CARGO 	ELEMENT 1 </Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER-FWD CARGO ELEMENT 2</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER 2-FWD CARGO ELEMENT 1</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>HEATER 2-FWD CARGO ELEMENT 2</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Set FCAC to OFF.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<Para>Forward cargo air conditioning is not available. Temperature sensitive cargo should not be carried in the forward cargo compartment. Refer to flight NOTOC for details.</Para>
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
</DispatchItems>